    ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════

    BONUS SECTOR - Advanced Training

    These terminals contain challenges designed by Earth's most demanding
    instructors. They are optional, but those who complete them emerge
    as truly elite operators.

    ┌─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┐
    │  AVAILABLE TRAINING MODULES:                                       │
    │                                                                    │
    │  • processes/   - Life Support Diagnostics (ps, grep, kill)       │
    │  • datalink/    - API Data Extraction (curl, jq)                  │
    │  • archives/    - Ship Log Version Control (git)                  │
    │                                                                    │
    │  Complete them in any order. Each builds different skills.         │
    └─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┘

